# Project separation — Portfolio Navigator Plus only

This workspace is **Portfolio Navigator Plus**, a **separate repository and product** from Cisco Portfolio Navigator (production).

## Always

- Make all code changes, commits, and pushes in **this repo** (`bnarcum/portfolio-navigator-plus`).
- Local path: `/Users/bnarcum/Projects/Portfolio Navigator Plus`
- Push to: `git push origin main` on this repo only.
- Read `PROJECT.md` for full boundaries.

## Never (unless the user explicitly asks for a production release)

- Edit, commit, or push to `/Users/bnarcum/Projects/Cursor Portfolio` or `cisco-portfolio-navigator`.
- Use the `cisco-portfolio-navigator-preview` preview repo or dual-remote preview workflows.
- Assume changes here affect https://bnarcum.github.io/cisco-portfolio-navigator/ — they do not.

## Optional

- Pull selected fixes from production via a read-only `upstream` remote (one-way, manual). See `PROJECT.md`.
